import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import './index.css'
import App from './App'
import {BrowserRouter} from 'react-router-dom';
import { Provider } from 'react';
ReactDOM.render(
 <Provider><BrowserRouter><App />
 </BrowserRouter> ,
 document.getElementById('root')</Provider>
  
)
